abstract: NFL Roundup; New York Jets running back Chris Ivory and cornerback Darrelle Revis may miss upcoming game against Philadelphia Eagles because of injuries; other football news noted.
lead_paragraph: As the Jets try to defeat the Philadelphia Eagles for the first time in franchise history on Sunday, they may be without some prominent players, including cornerback Darrelle Revis.

headline.main: Darrelle Revis and Two Other Top Jets May Miss Game Against Eagles
headline.print_headline: Revis, Ivory and Decker May Be Out Vs. Eagles
